		<h3>Step 5</h3>
		<h4>Since you have the answers, now it is all actions</h4>
		<ul>
		<li>Raise Funds</li>
		<li>Announce Candidacy</li>
		<li>Use your media contacts that you created in previous step</li>
		<li>Gain early support of local political leaders assuming you made enough contact with them in previous step</li>
		<li>Broaden your physical base contacts using the virtual base contacts created in previous step</li>
		<li>Gain votes by arranging Face to Face meet. This is the key!!! </li>
		<li>Stick to the answers that you found in previous step as they are your CAMPAIGN PLAN. </li>
		
		</ul>
